data.description: Welcome to this charming 3 bed, 2 bath tri-level home, a perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Nestled against a wide open green space, this back yard promises privacy. As you step inside you'll be greeted by warm laminated floors and grand steps to the living room. The heart of this home includes an open kitchen with a functional island. New exterior siding and paint on the back side of the home. Fenced in back yard! Ready to show Saturday December 2nd!
